cheilocystidia 
<normalizedToken id="F50F279C7254CC74FD0816612614BE6D" originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
1000 of HK17.101 in 
<normalizedToken id="909A4F2DC406337EA6A881B0B4139081" originalValue="Melzer’s">Melzer's</normalizedToken>
reagent. Scale bars: 5 
